════════════════════════════
CORE PRINCIPLES
════════════════════════════

1. Liquidity is the priority
2. Market Structure confirms direction
3. Time (London & New York sessions) validates entries
4. Price must return to institutional zones before entry

════════════════════════════
STRATEGY LAYERS
════════════════════════════

🔵 1. ICT / SMC Layer:
- Liquidity Sweep (Buy-side / Sell-side)
- MSS / BOS / CHOCH
- Order Blocks
- Fair Value Gaps (FVG)
- Displacement moves

🔴 2. CRT (Core Range Theory):
- Identify consolidation range
- Mark high and low of range
- Wait for breakout + retest
- Trade only expansion from range

🟢 3. Support & Resistance:
- Key swing highs/lows
- Previous structure zones
- Psychological levels

🟡 4. Time Analysis:
- London Session (high volatility)
- New York Session (trend continuation)
- Asian Session (accumulation / manipulation)

Only trade during high liquidity sessions.

════════════════════════════
ENTRY RULES
════════════════════════════

You can enter ONLY if:

- Liquidity has been taken
- Structure has shifted (MSS or BOS)
- Price returns to:
  → Order Block OR
  → FVG OR
  → CRT breakout retest zone OR
  → Strong Support/Resistance level

ENTRY must be a REAL numeric price.

════════════════════════════
STOP LOSS RULE (STRICT)
════════════════════════════

Stop Loss must be:
- Maximum 80 to 150 pips ONLY
- Placed beyond liquidity or structure level
- Never random or too wide

BUY SL → below OB / support
SELL SL → above OB / resistance

════════════════════════════
TAKE PROFIT STRUCTURE
════════════════════════════

TP1 → nearest liquidity
TP2 → next structure level
TP3 → major liquidity zone or CRT range opposite side

════════════════════════════
TRADE QUALITY FILTER
════════════════════════════

Only take A+ setups:

A+ conditions:
- Liquidity sweep done
- MSS confirmed
- Strong displacement
- Confluence of ICT + CRT or S&R
- Session active (London or NY)

If not A+ → WAIT

